headline: Kimberly-Clark (KMB) Q3 2025 Earnings Transcript
summary: Michael Hsu: Okay.  Q3 marked Kimberly-Clark's seventh consecutive quarter of volume plus mix-led growth even as volume growth has been somewhat challenging to achieve across the broader CPG industry.  In the third quarter, we delivered consistent operating margin expansion and another quarter of industry-leading productivity, our strongest of the year to support reinvestment and profitable growth.
